headline: Synopsys Links Chiplet IP To Lightmatter Optics For Future AI Data Centers
summary: Synopsys (NasdaqGS:SNPS) and Lightmatter are collaborating to integrate Synopsys' 224G SerDes and UCIe IP into Lightmatter's 3D Co-Packaged Optics platform. The partnership focuses on high bandwidth, low latency connectivity for AI accelerators used in next generation AI infrastructure. The agreement centers on integrating chiplet based connectivity standards like UCIe with photonic computing to support data intensive AI workloads.
